<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l15"><expan>aufgeſlag<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd etwıeuıl hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l16">eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſſ / den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . eẅr gnade hılff vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l17"><expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> . vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wıllen darinn <expan>ʒubeweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> da mıt ſıe ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_453_r1l18"><expan>Jr<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mugen . als etc / das wellen etc </ab>
