<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> etwievil
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt fürbracht, wie in yecz in kürcz
                        zwischem Hof und Zwickaw etlich wegen <expan>aufgeslag<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und etwievil hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey
                            <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>; <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss, den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr gnade, hilff und
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        willen darinn <expan>zu beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>, damit sie zu
                                <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> mugen. Als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
